- # HorizCoin
-
- HorizCoin is a blockchain protocol implementing a Proof-of-Bandwidth consensus mechanism. This repository contains the reference implementation of the HorizCoin node software, wallet, and development tools.
-
- ## Quick Start
-
- ### Prerequisites
-
-   * Rust 1.70+ with Cargo
-   * Git
- ### Building
-
-     # Clone the repository
-     git clone https://github.com/thehorizonholding/HorizCoin.git
-     cd HorizCoin
-
-     # Set Rust version for project
-     rustup override set 1.70.0
-
-     # Build all components
-     cargo build --workspace
-
-     # Run the node
-     cargo run -p horizcoin-node
-
-     # Run the CLI (see help)
-     cargo run -p horiz-cli -- --help
-
-     # Run tests
-     cargo test
+ # HorizCoin
+
+ HorizCoin is a blockchain protocol implementing a Proof-of-Bandwidth consensus mechanism. This repository contains a reference implementation of the HorizCoin node, CLI tools, and a small web demo.
+
+ ## Quick Start (tested)
+
+ ### Prerequisites
+ - Rust (recommended: 1.70 via rustup; this project builds with `rustup override set 1.70.0`)
+ - Cargo (comes with Rust)
+ - Git
+ - Docker (for containerized builds)
+ - Node.js (LTS, recommended 18.x or 20.x) and npm (for the web UI)
+
+ **Tip:** Use rustup and nvm to pin toolchain versions for reproducible builds.
+
+ ### Build and run (local - Rust workspace)
+ ```bash
+ # Clone
+ git clone https://github.com/thehorizonholding/HorizCoin.git
+ cd HorizCoin
+
+ # Pin rust toolchain (optional)
+ rustup override set 1.70.0
+
+ # Build the full workspace
+ cargo build --workspace --release
+
+ # Run the node (example)
+ cargo run -p horizcoin-node --release
+ ```
+
+ ### Run the CLI
+ ```bash
+ # See flags and commands
+ cargo run -p horiz-cli -- --help
+ ```
+
+ ### Run the web demo (Node)
+ ```bash
+ cd web || true
+ npm install
+ npm run start
+ # or (production)
+ npm run build
+ npm start
+ ```
+
+ ### Docker (recommended for demo)
+ ```bash
+ docker build -t horizcoin-web .
+ docker run -p 3000:3000 -e PORT=3000 horizcoin-web
+ ```
+
+ ### Run tests
+ ```bash
+ cargo test --workspace
+ ```
+
+ ### Trouble-shooting
+ - If a build fails due to Rust edition or toolchain mismatch, run `rustup toolchain install 1.70.0`.
+ - If Node packages fail, remove `node_modules` and reinstall with `npm ci`.
+
